Shaping Life Through Immersive Sound.
Show us your adventures with #sudio and #shapingsound

node.text: Thank you to @hisbrownpoet for creating this amazing video featuring Sudio Ett! We are proud to celebrate our black creatives/collaborators 🎶

node.text:
"In 2019, Sudio set the goal of becoming a carbon neutral organisation. We are working with a third party organisation, Carbon Footprint Ltd, to ensure that we are a 100% carbon neutral organisation. Sudio has additionally chosen to offset our calculated carbon dioxide output by donating to Escarpment Environment Conservation Network (Esconet) which is an organisation that focuses on the restoration of the Great Rift Valley in Kenya."⁠♻️⁠
⁠
Read more about our goal to become carbon neutral on our website under "Our Story."⁠🌱⁠
@theresaskjolden #sudio #shapingsound #ett-green
